lead_paragraph: Jeff Green scored a season-high 30 points, Memphis converted enough free throws in an extra period and the Grizzlies defeated the Orlando Magic 108-102 in overtime Monday night.

headline.print_headline: Green Scores Season-High 30 as Grizzlies Beat Magic 108-102
